            "url_slug": "Shipping FAQ",
            "icon": "delivery",
            "section_heading": "Shipping FAQ",
            "section_description": "",
            "question_1": "How will my order be shipped?",
            "answer_1": "<p>USA shipping option:</p><ul><li>USPS $6.98 - (5-9 Business Days after fulfillment)</li></ul><p>Please note, we take anywhere from 2-5 business days to process and fulfill your order. The shipping times above are calculated after your order leaves our warehouse.</p><p>For international shipping, please see the tab below.</p>",
            "question_2": "Do you ship internationally?",
            "answer_2": "<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Yes we do (certain countries may be excluded).</span></p><p>We ship within 2-5 business days from the order date. We offer international shipping: UPS Standard (time frame depends on the country, it will be indicated at checkout).</p>",
            "question_3": "Do you ship to PO boxes?",
            "answer_3": "<p>Yes, we do ship to PO boxes. Please make sure your box is large enough to receive a package.</p>",
            "question_4": "Do you ship to hotels?",
            "answer_4": "<p>For the best delivery experience, we do not ship to hotel addresses. Unfortunately, packages sent to hotels are often returned or lost, and in these cases we’re unable to offer refunds or replacements.</p>",
            "question_5": "What happens to 'returned to sender' and/or unclaimed packages?",
            "answer_5": "<p>It is a customer’s responsibility to provide the correct shipping address and to track the order using the tracking number we provide in the shipping confirmation email.  We encourage you to always check your SPAM and JUNK email folders as confirmation emails sometimes tend to end up there. If you are moving, please notify us of the new shipping address by contacting help@baudie.com even if you have mail forwarding set up. If an order is returned back to us due to insufficient address, forwarding issues or if the package was unclaimed, once we receive the package back at our warehouse, we will issue a refund minus the shipping charges (as the shipping charges go directly to the carrier). We can not be responsible for re-shipping the unclaimed and/or insufficient address packages.  If you have tracked your package and can see that is was returned back to us, please email help@baudie.com to notify us.</p>",
            "question_6": "Where is my package? It was marked \"delivered\" but I didn't receive it.",
            "answer_6": "<p>Sometimes tracking information can be incorrect and packages are marked as delivered before they actually arrive. Your package will most likely be delivered within 3 business days from the marked delivery date, but here are some tips to try in the meantime:</p><p>-First check to see if the carrier left a notice of attempted delivery. Sometimes carriers are unable to deliver a package if you aren’t home. They will typically make 3 delivery attempts before returning to sender.</p><p>-Look around to see if it was left nearby and ask your neighbors in case it was delivered to them instead of you.</p><p>-See if another member of the household accepted the delivery.</p><p>-Check your mailbox, most of our packages fit into a mailbox. </p><p>Any packages that are marked \"delivered\" that you have not received, <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">must be reported to us within 5 days of the official delivery scan</span>. Please report by emailing help@baudie.com . We always send out an email with tracking information. It is the customer's responsibility to track their order closely.  </p><p>It is a customer’s responsibility to provide the correct address that the shipping carrier is able to deliver to.  If the shipping carrier is unable to deliver to the address that the customer provided, the customer has to resolve the delivery issue with the shipping carrier directly.  If the package gets returned to us as undeliverable, a customer can choose to either have the package resent for a re-shipment fee of $6.98 (USA) or $19.98 (International) or receive a refund in the amount that was originally paid minus the shipping fee originally paid.</p>",
            "question_7": "I received my tracking information but there are no transit updates/scans.",
            "answer_7": "<p>Tracking scans can take up to 72 hours to update on the shipping carrier websites. We do our best to ensure the timely delivery of all orders. We are not able to provide a specific delivery date as we do not have this information from our carriers. Occasionally packages can arrive later than expected.</p>",
            "question_8": "What do I do if I received the wrong product?",
            "answer_8": "<p>We must be notified within 5 days of package delivery. We will ask for additional information and will resolve it for you.</p>",
