            "section_heading": "Returns FAQ",
            "section_description": "",
            "question_1": "What is your USA return policy?",
            "answer_1": "<p>Our goal is to help you find the products that are the perfect fit for your skin, health & lifestyle. We hope you’ll be completely satisfied with your products and if you are not, we <strong>will accept a return for up to 3 items in a singular order (if purchasing a bundle, every item in the bundle counts) for a refund or store credit as long as the products are at least 80% full and shipped back within 30 days of initial purchase date</strong>. <strong>Only 3 items per person per 12 month period are eligible for a return. </strong>Please note the origional shipping cost is non-refundable.</p><ul><li>PLEASE NOTE: The Face Sampler Set, Underarm Toner Duo in Travel Size (Create your own duo), and singular MINI Underarm Toners are <strong>NOT ELIGIBLE FOR A RETURN OR STORE CREDIT</strong>. They are <strong>FINAL SALE</strong>.</li><li>If a promotional code was used at the time of purchase, the refund or store credit will reflect the prorated amount of each discounted item requesting to be returned.</li></ul><p>We monitor return and refund activity and reserve the right to limit or refuse a return or charge a return processing fee if we find that our policies have been abused. Any finding of abuse of our policies shall be in our sole discretion and is not appealable. We are not obligated to disclose our reasons and methods, other than to inform the consumer that the refund request is being refused for abuse of our return policy. <strong>Note that any returns sent in that were not authorized by our team and do not meet the return criteria will be recycled/disposed of.</strong></p>",
            "question_2": "What is your international return policy?",
            "answer_2": "<p>At this time, we are not able to offer returns or exchanges for international orders due to new intricate tariff policies.</p>",
            "question_3": "How do I initiate a return?",
            "answer_3": "<p>To initiate a return/store credit please email <strong>help@baudie.com</strong>.</p><ul><li>There will be a fee of up to <strong>$12 deducted from the refund</strong> to cover return/handling costs. This fee will depend upon how many items you are returning in your order.</li></ul><p><strong>If you choose to receive store credit, you will not be charged the return/handling fee.</strong></p>",
            "question_4": "Can I return a single item in a bundle or collection?",
            "answer_4": "<p>If you purchased a bundle/collection on our website and you want to return some of the items in the bundle/collection, you may do so according to our return policy.</p><p>However, the price of the item you are keeping reverts to the full listed price of that item. The refund for the returned items will be adjusted accordingly.</p><ul><li>PLEASE NOTE: The Face Sampler Set, Underarm Toner Travel Pack (Create your own duo), and singular MINI Underarm Toners are <strong>NOT ELIGIBLE FOR A RETURN OR STORE CREDIT</strong>. They are <strong>FINAL SALE</strong>.</li></ul>",
            "question_5": "What if I recevied a gift with purchase but still need to make a return?",
            "answer_5": "<p>If your return brings your order subtotal below the threshold for a free gift, the gift must also be returned unused.</p>",
            "question_6": "How soon will I get my refund?",
            "answer_6": "<p>A store credit or refund will be processed within 7 business days. You’ll receive a confirmation via email as soon as it’s been processed. Please note, it can take several days for the refund to be reflected on your bank account statement.</p><p>Store credit is issued in the form of a gift card that does not expire.</p>",
            "question_7": "Can I return products I purchased with a gift card?",
            "answer_7": "<p>Any orders purchased with a gift card will receive<strong>store credit only</strong>if returned according to our return policy.</p>",
            "question_8": "How do I cancel/modify my order?",
            "answer_8": "<p>At this time, we are unable to modify an order after it has been placed. We only allow order cancellations within 3 hours of placing the order (you must email us to help@baudie.com within 3 hours of placing your order for the cancellation to be valid).</p>",
